sentences: Jon began piano lessons at the age of five and trumpet and violin lessons at ten years of age.
The Brian Blade Fellowship album Season of Changes was released around 2008.
Cowherd also worked with Brian Blade in his debut singer-songwriter album Mama Rosa, which was released in 2009 on Verve Records.
Cowherd's debut album as a leader, Mercy,  was released in 2013 on ArtistShare.
